contentrichtext.text: {{Wiktionary}} '''Kickstart''' can refer to: * [[kick start]], the task of using the foot activated starter (the ''kickstarter'') on a motorcycle * ''[[Kick Start]]'', an album by the English band The Lambrettas * [[Kickstart (Amiga)]], the bootstrap of the Amiga computers developed by Commodore * [[Kickstart (Linux)]], a network installation system for some Linux distributions * [[Kick Start (TV series)|''Kick Start'' (TV series)]], a UK television series on motor bike competitions, and a spinoff computer game * [[Yahoo! Kickstart]], a professional network from Yahoo! * [[Kickstarter]], an online funding platform for creative projects * Kickstart, [[Homes and Communities Agency]] funding programme for private housing in the UK * [[Kickstarts (song)|"Kickstarts" (song)]], a song by Example * [[KICKSTART]], a charity association * [[Kickstart (orthosis)]] {{disambig}}
